      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Question:\nHow to create a project from scratch to use the Renesas Flash Driver RL78 Type 01 on RL78/G2x devices ?\n  Answer:"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "How to create a project from scratch to use the Renesas Flash Driver RL78 Type 01 on RL78/G2x devices ?"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "How to create a project from scratch to use the Renesas Flash Driver RL78 Type 01 on RL78/G2x devices ?"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Answer:"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "To create a project from scratch to use the Renesas Flash Driver RL78 Type 01 on RL78/G2x devices, do the following steps:"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "1) Add the r_rfd_rl78_t01_dataflash and r_rfd_rl78_t01_common components on the Smart Configurator:"
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "content": {
          "original_url": "https://en-support.renesas.com/api/attachments/action/1/c1b3d1f0-6a30-422f-8ee0-9400fc5b0e9a",
          "alt_text": "",
          "width": "602",
          "height": "850",
          "local_path": "data/categories/rl78_family/rl78g23/03331522dd20eff998b20d765a566138/images/4db65c38cf33c645f83de180a80b6f68.png"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "2) Set the following option to enable the data flash access:"
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "content": {
          "original_url": "https://en-support.renesas.com/api/attachments/action/1/447e0cdb-192f-4478-9c58-0e4badb46e22",
          "alt_text": "",
          "width": "1104",
          "height": "624",
          "local_path": "data/categories/rl78_family/rl78g23/03331522dd20eff998b20d765a566138/images/b681e3b990a3229d9da87b1e55c3e3ad.png"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "3) Add the following sections in ROM and RAM memory which will be used by the Renesas Flash Driver RL78 Type 01."
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "content": {
          "original_url": "https://en-support.renesas.com/api/attachments/action/1/daf8a149-fe68-4a2e-9c56-21cc3091a947",
          "alt_text": "",
          "width": "980",
          "height": "910",
          "local_path": "data/categories/rl78_family/rl78g23/03331522dd20eff998b20d765a566138/images/3494f51a5c7fb14e874b6f956a4af8f7.png"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "4) Add the following -rom option for RFD_DATA_n section which will be copied into RAM."
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "content": {
          "original_url": "https://en-support.renesas.com/api/attachments/action/1/c2a7f023-4239-439e-b579-845a24b53a73",
          "alt_text": "",
          "width": "980",
          "height": "910",
          "local_path": "data/categories/rl78_family/rl78g23/03331522dd20eff998b20d765a566138/images/0f07395cc8db5f719f760ab76668e528.png"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "5) Refer to the attached project for RL78/G23 FPB 64-pin board on how to add code to initialize the flash library and perform the basic data flash operations (blank check/erase/write)."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "You can find all information for the Renesas Flash Driver RL78 Type 01 User's Manual for RL78/G2x on the user's manual:"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "https://www.renesas.com/en/document/man/renesas-flash-driver-rl78-type-01-users-manual-rl78g23"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Suitable Products"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "RL78/G23"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "RL78/G23"
      }
